Debra/Weydert/CORPHQ/NYTIMES(at)nytimes.com. If unable to reach Ms.
Weydert, please call 800-444-0267, or fax us at 816-822-1444.)  
  
 (ATTN. EDITORS: FOR THOSE DESIRING A SHORTER VERSION, THIS
EXTENSIVE ARTICLE CAN STAND IN 1,150 WORDS. TOTAL UNCUT VERSION IS
1,300.)  
  
