<P>
   ONLINE-RELIEF (Undated) _ On-line volunteer organization, the
Sunflowers, run by a Dutchman who organized relief in Bosnia and
Croatia, is getting thousands of people worldwide to travel to
refugee camps to do the kind of nonessential things the big relief
groups don't get to do. By Patti Hartigan. 1200 words.
</P>
