   KOSOVO-PRISTINA (Pristina) _ An interview with the Serb who
heads the interim executive council that runs Kosovo. By Steven
Erlanger.
</P>
<P>
   We are considering, among others, stories on developments,
diplomatic and otherwise, in Brussels, Belgrade and at the United
Nations; and the arrival at Fort Dix, N.J., of more Kosovo
refugees.
