<HEADLINE>


</HEADLINE>
  The Los Angeles Daily News plans to move the following sports
stories for use by NYTimes News Service clients, AMs and PMs of May
8 and thereafter. For questions about stories, resends or
inquiries, call Joe Jares at (818) 713-3602. 
 
 
BBN-DODGERS (Los Angeles) _ Los Angeles Dodgers play host to the
Florida Marlins, 7:10 p.m. 
