<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-OLY-ATLANTA-PROBE-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;    
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    House begins inquiry into Atlanta's bid
 &HT;    By Melissa Turner
